{"tid":740484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會考25分女生轉人生軌道　不做會計做焊接職安女漢子","createTime":"2018-07-13T02:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T01:48:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"73b225c026d1ca2cc9ea4ffb8934ff8710d680a9","tid":740484,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2109790/choi_thumb_20180711_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2109790%2Fchoi_thumb_20180711_J_1024.jpg&h=6f2de0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地盤彷彿是「男人的天下」，焊接電光火石間更加是男人的主場。90後外表甜美斯文的蔡娟娟，當年會考考獲25分，順利升讀大學會計系，畢業後卻毫不猶豫地轉投焊接業，成為香港少數的女性焊接檢驗師。轉換人生跑道，她只淡然地解釋：「不想一世對住數字」。<br />\n<br />\n留著長曲髮的娟娟，化上淡妝，與地盤服裝看似格格不入。她笑說，中四至中七修讀會計，會考成績25分，順理成章考入香港理工大學會計系，直至找了份會計的實習工作，她領悟到自己對會計熱情不大...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2109790/%E6%9C%83%E8%80%8325%E5%88%86%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E8%BB%8C%E9%81%93%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%81%9A%E7%84%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%B3%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2109790%2F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2580%258325%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25BD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25BB%258C%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%2584%258A%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590&d=HEH8e4qRqfSiWwmKscOQDAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=48fbdb50\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2109790/%E6%9C%83%E8%80%8325%E5%88%86%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E8%BB%8C%E9%81%93%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%81%9A%E7%84%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%B3%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%90</a>"},{"pid":"8b8a58b7b6d140da52c4dd